Inquire Now
Weddings/Rehearsals
Picture yourself surrounded by the natural beauty of the ocean, with the sun setting behind you as you say "I do". Your guests will be in awe of the stunning waterfront views and the peaceful sounds of the islands . With both outdoor & indoor event spaces for your guests, there is no bad time of year to get married in our slice of paradise!
Group Packages
If you're planning a large tour or group event in the Florida Keys, it's your time to CHILL! With beautiful waterfront locations that can accommodate groups of any size, our team will help plan every detail of your event. We offer a variety of catering options, including group package rates!
Corporate Events & Buyouts
Looking to hold a corporate event or even buyout an entire waterfront destination in the Florida Keys? We've got the perfect venue for you! With a large variety of event space, we can accommodate any group size! Our team will help you plan every detail of your event, from the menu to the entertainment, ensuring that your next event in paradise is a success!
Proposals
Imagine walking down the beach with your significant other. As you turn around, you see your partner down on one knee, holding out a ring and asking you to spend the rest of your life with them. The colors of the sunset create a beautiful backdrop for this special moment, and the sound of the ocean provides a peaceful and romantic ambiance. This proposal will be a memory that you will cherish forever.
Auto Clubs
Looking for a place for your car, motorcycle, boat, or jet ski club? With access by land or by sea, we have tons of options and parking for any of your auto club needs!

About Us
Located at Mile Marker 104, Bayside in Key Largo. Jimmy Johnson's Big Chill offers waterfront entertainment and dining 7 days a week while taking in breathtaking Sunset Views of the Florida Bay. Home to The Big Chill Restaurant & Tiki Bar, JJ's Sport's Bar, JJ's Pool & Cabana Club, Enrico's Pizza, Jimmy Johnson's Official Store & Pirates Cove Watersports!

Hall Of Fame Coach Jimmy Johnson
Former Dallas Cowboys, Miami Dolphins, and University of Miami football coach Jimmy Johnson has had a residence in the Florida Keys since just after his second Super Bowl victory. He moved to his current home in Islamorada two decades ago and his name graces Jimmy Johnson's Big Chill at Fisherman's Cove, a dining and entertainment complex in Key Largo.

Enrico's New York Style Pizza
Enrico Michael Calvano, father of Larry Calvano, owner and operator of The Big Chill, was one of the Masters of the Art of making pizza. He and his wife opened their first pizza restaurant in New York City in the early '60's, and after many successful years moved to the beautiful state of Florida with their three young children. In 1972, they moved to Fort Lauderdale and Enrico's New York Style Pizza was born. The Calvano family is carrying on Enrico's legacy at The Big Chill, and when it comes to pizza here, it's about pride, passion, and a combined family experience of over 100 years. Enrico's New York Style Pizza at Jimmy Johnson's Big Chill is committed to serving only the finest, freshest ingredients in our pizzas. True Italian pizzas the way it should be, and our way of saying Grazie Key Largo!
